==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: five-spot
<hw>five-spot</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
California annual (<spn>Nemophila maculata</spn>) having white flowers
with a deep purple blotch on each petal.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> five spot, <spn>Nemophila maculata</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a playing card or a domino or a die whose upward
face shows five pips.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A five-dollar bill.</def> <mark>[U. S.
slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Five-twenties</ent>⟦br⟧
